         <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">

         	<p n="1-2">
         		Seventh year of the victorious king Mahendravarman<note>May<sic>a</sic>ntiraparumaṉ in the original Tamil text.</note>.
         	</p>

         	<p n="2-13">
         		<supplied reason="subaudible">This is</supplied> the stone of Ēṟaṉ, son of <gap reason="ellipsis"/>, he who died <gap reason="ellipsis"/> <supplied reason="subaudible">fighthing</supplied> with<note>That is, at the side of or against.</note> Kaṅkati Araicar <supplied reason="subaudible">at/of</supplied> Kārimaṅkalam in the Kōvūrnāṭu.</p>


         </div>

